Sentencas: Ni-based anode supports with straight open pores were well prepared using self-organization process.
Titulo: Preparation and evaluation of Ni-based anodes with straight open pores for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The scanning electron microscopy (SEM) results of YSZ ceramic skeletons showed that honeycomb-like structures with highly ordered straight pores were obtained.
Titulo: Preparation and evaluation of Ni-based anodes with straight open pores for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The regulation of solid loading and CaCl2 concentration on the morphology of YSZ skeletons were discussed.
Titulo: Preparation and evaluation of Ni-based anodes with straight open pores for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The YSZ skeleton with solid loading of 10 wt% and CaCl2 concentration of 1.5 mol L(-1 )delivered a pore size of 99 mu m and a porosity of 46.9%.
Titulo: Preparation and evaluation of Ni-based anodes with straight open pores for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The solid oxide fuel cell based on Ni-YSZ anode possessed a maximum power density of 253 mW cm(-2) and an ohmic resistance of 0.16 Omega cm(2) at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Preparation and evaluation of Ni-based anodes with straight open pores for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The pore diameter and porosity of the ceramic supports could be adjusted to expected values by further optimization of the parameters.
Titulo: Preparation and evaluation of Ni-based anodes with straight open pores for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The self-organization method will become a feasible and valid operation to produce anode supports with appropriate morphologies.
Titulo: Preparation and evaluation of Ni-based anodes with straight open pores for solid oxide fuel cells
